{
  "stem": "20575.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They brought us to to Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And it was March, beginning of April.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Again, no food, nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They let us out occasionally from the trains to go on the-- underneath the train to have your, your functions.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I remember there were cherry blossom trees-- cherry trees, you know, on the side of the train.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we went-- we ate the cherry blossoms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We ate grass.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And whatever water there was, we took and we drank it, whatever, whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So we figured, you know, it's good for the animals.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It'll be good for-- I mean, good for us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We, we needed to have something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Until we-- all of a sudden, we looked, and we saw Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "That-- the train went into Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Well, we knew about Mauthausen coming from Austria because Mauthausen was one of the oldest concentration camps in Austria.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "It was a quarry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And a lot of [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] political prisoners were there already long before and a lot of criminals, murderers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "It was like a, a, a-- in a prison.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And somehow, somehow, we thought, maybe-- oh, we are in Austria.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Maybe it won't be so bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "As we lined up-- as we lined up the road there to go into the camp, all the locals were standing left and right, laughing and saying, well, that's a good place for you.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "There you will-- you will find your eternal rest here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "That's what they told us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "This was-- these were the Austrians, the good Austrians that-- they say they didn't know-- like, the surrounding people who didn't know that there was a camp.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And we went up there, terrible afraid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "We were concentrated in one area.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And it says, we're going to take a bath.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "We're going to take a shower.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And I started crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
